## Task: V2: Domain model — Task and Attempt types

Add Task and Attempt as first-class domain types in internal/domain/. Task has ID, Title, Status (derived from latest attempt), source (external/user-initiated). Attempt has ID (random 4-char alphanumeric, unique within task), TaskID, StartedAt, EndedAt, Result. Refactor the existing Run struct to become a step execution linked to an Attempt. See docs/plans/2026-03-18-task-oriented-apis-design.md.
